Review: Needed my therapy driedel 4 times during this film. They call this a comedy but I think they forgot to add the jokes. Yeah, I dont get it, maybe thats on me, but this picture is as funny as the Spanish inquistion. Its well shot, its interesting, it just went over my head completely and utterly. Is it my fault? Hell no! Is it the films fault? Also no. I blame God.
Undeniably charming but ultimately not very funny. John Candy was the fucking man though
